com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.photostructures

Class ThumbPhoto

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.photostructures.ThumbPhoto
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FullPhoto

    public class ThumbPhoto
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that hold the basic info of the thumb photo, hold the id, resolution and the link of the the thumb photo as well full res photo.
